---
title: Carb Smart Almond Tofu with Green Veggies and Lemony Mayo
description: In a dish inspired by Parmesan chicken, tender tofu is topped with a Parmesan crust, and we've swapped breadcrumbs out for almonds to keep those carbs low. A tumble of garlicky green veggies is always a good idea.

Carb Smart (50 g carbohydrates or less) is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's carbohydrate amount.
